    <summary>Local-first desktop PDF studio (viewer, editor, OCR).</summary>
    <description><![CDATA[
LocalPDF Studio is a local-first desktop PDF viewer and utility suite built with Tauri 2 + React.

**Features**:
- View / search / outline / thumbnails
- Merge / split / encrypt / compress
- OCR via Tesseract (auto-installed) + Searchable PDF generation
- Page editor (reorder / delete / rotate / insert)
- Metadata editing, form filling, bookmarks, side-by-side compare
- Watermark / stamp
- Auto-update via Tauri updater (signed)

All processing is performed locally — no cloud uploads.

**External tools** (auto-installed via in-app installer):
- qpdf (for PDF manipulation)
- Tesseract OCR (for searchable PDF / text extraction)
]]></description>
    <releaseNotes>https://github.com/jeiel85/localpdf-studio/releases/tag/v0.17.0</releaseNotes>
